{"word":"G501 - ἀντλέω - antléō - ant-leh-o - Draw","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀντλέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">antléō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ant-leh-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Draw</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தண்ணீர் மொள்ளுதல்"},{"paragraph":"to draw water"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x0301;&#x03BD;&#x03C4;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03C2;</b> <b>antlos</b> (the <i>hold</i> of a ship); to <i>bale</i> up (properly bilge water), that is, <i>dip</i> water (with a bucket, pitcher, etc.): - draw (out).</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}